obj_dw_churchc_angelprophecy_encounter_s: * Treasure? There is no treasure..^1. only experience./
* The other side of your mind..^1. did you miss something there?/
* We are all liars now. Yes^1, it's fun being a liar./%
* It's absolutely true. Oh^1, sink me^1, the unbeliever. I should be a statue./%
* Of course you didn't. There's nothing to miss./
* Those who can't speak the truth are liars./
* And none of us can know the truth now^1, so we're all liars!/
* Look for yourself^1! There's nothing back there^1, is there?/%
* Liar^1! Your hands are shining. You took and made^1, took and made./
* Tickets and cards^1, drawn in gray^1, a trace - repeated^1, repeated^1! - it's all so clear!/
* ..^1. though^1, it would be a lie if I said I understood it!/%
* You speak the truth so confidently./
* You are safe now^1, but you have the makings of a liar./%
